### HCP CRM AI - Smoke Tests
### Use with VS Code REST Client or HTTPie

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

---

### 2. Get All HCPs
GET {{baseUrl}}/hcps/
Accept: application/json

---

### 3. Create Interaction (Structured Form bypassing NLU)
POST {{baseUrl}}/interactions/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "hcp_id": 1,
  "rep_id": "demo_rep",
  "interaction_date": "2026-07-15",
  "channel": "in-person",
  "topics_discussed": ["Efficacy", "Dosage"],
  "products_discussed": ["WonderDrug"],
  "sentiment": "positive",
  "samples_given": {"WonderDrug": 5},
  "follow_up_required": true,
  "follow_up_date": "2026-07-22",
  "summary": "Met with Dr. Smith. Very positive feedback on WonderDrug.",
  "raw_input": "Manual Form Entry",
  "source": "form"
}

---

### 4. Get Interactions for an HCP (assuming HCP ID 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/interactions/1
Accept: application/json

---

### 5. Edit an Interaction (assuming Interaction ID 1)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/interactions/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sentiment": "neutral",
  "samples_given": {"WonderDrug": 10},
  "summary": "Updated summary: Sentiment was neutral, gave 10 samples."
}

---

### 6. Schedule Follow-up
POST {{baseUrl}}/follow-ups/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "interaction_id": 1,
  "due_date": "2026-07-29",
  "status": "pending",
  "note": "Send clinical trial data."
}

---

### 7. Chat Endpoint (Testing LangGraph Agent)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "I just met with Dr. Smith. We discussed the new side effects of HealPill. He was neutral. I gave him 2 samples. Please remind me to follow up next Friday.",
  "session_id": "session_123"
}
